OL,3,CJohn Swinney calls on parties to agree
OL,4,Cbudget quickly
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister has urged
OL,7,Fparties in Holyrood to reach agreement
OL,8,Fon the budget quickly to provide
OL,9,Fcertainty to public services.
OL,11,FFinance Secretary Shona Robison will
OL,12,Flay out the Government's tax and
OL,13,Fspending plans on January 13 in a
OL,14,Fprocess shortened by the lateness of
OL,15,Fthe UK Government Budget in November.
