OL,3,CJohn Swinney calls on parties to agree
OL,4,Cbudget quickly
OL,6,FSpeaking to the Press Association,
OL,7,FJohn Swinney pushed for parties to
OL,8,Fwork quickly to reach a deal which
OL,9,Fwill get the budget over the line as
OL,10,Fthe Government looks to secure "broad
OL,11,Fagreement" ahead of the Bill facing
OL,12,Fits final stage in early March.
OL,14,F"One of the things that I am concerned
OL,15,Fabout is that that truncates the
OL,16,Fnotice about budget that can be
OL,17,Favailable to a lot of organisations,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
