OL,3,CJohn Swinney calls on parties to agree
OL,4,Cbudget quickly
OL,6,F"We'll be working to try to create as
OL,7,Fmuch certainty as early as we possibly
OL,8,Fcan do because that will be beneficial
OL,9,Ffor countless organisations,
OL,10,Fprincipally third sector organisations
OL,11,Fand local authorities, about what the
OL,12,Ffunding level is going to be next
OL,13,Fyear."
OL,15,FAt the UK Budget, Chancellor Rachel
OL,16,FReeves announced plans to scrap the
OL,17,Ftwo-child benefit cap, freeing up cash
OL,18,Ffor the Scottish Government, which had
OL,19,Falready pledged tens of millions to
OL,20,Fmitigate the policy north of the
OL,21,Fborder.
