OL,3,CJohn Swinney calls on parties to agree
OL,4,Cbudget quickly
OL,6,FBefore the announcement, the First
OL,7,FMinister said any savings made as a
OL,8,Fresult of the cap being scrapped would
OL,9,Fbe re-invested in initiatives aimed at
OL,10,Freducing child poverty, what he has
OL,11,Fdescribed as his Government's
OL,12,Foverarching mission.
